---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  lang="en"
  title="Privacy Notice – My Light Art Gallery"
  description="Privacy Notice for https://www.mylightartgallery.com"
>
  <section class="privacy">
    <div class="privacy-scroll-fade" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Privacy Notice</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        This notice applies to https://www.mylightartgallery.com and services provided by LATCOM,
        5215 N. O&apos;Connor Rd. Ste 1725, Irving, TX 75039, United States. Tel: +1 (972) 444-4553.
      </p>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Controller</h2>
        <p><strong>Legal entity:</strong> LATCOM</p>
        <p><strong>Address:</strong> 5215 N. O&apos;Connor Rd. Ste 1725, Irving, TX 75039, United States.</p>
        <p><strong>Phone:</strong> +1 (972) 444-4553</p>
        <p><strong>Site:</strong> https://www.mylightartgallery.com</p>
        <p><strong>Privacy contact:</strong> privacy@mylightartgallery.com</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Personal data we collect</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Identification and contact: name, email, phone.</li>
          <li>Browsing/usage: IP, device identifiers, cookies, analytics.</li>
          <li>Transactions: orders, payment method (processed by third parties), purchase history.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Purposes</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Service delivery (accounts, orders, deliveries).</li>
          <li>Customer support and communications (inquiries, newsletter with consent).</li>
          <li>Security and fraud prevention.</li>
          <li>Analytics and site improvement (cookies/tech). </li>
          <li>Marketing with consent where applicable.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Legal bases (GDPR)</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Contract or precontractual steps.</li>
          <li>Legitimate interest (security, fraud prevention, service improvement).</li>
          <li>Consent (non-essential cookies, marketing).</li>
          <li>Legal obligation (tax/accounting retention).</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Transfers and third parties</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Payment, hosting, analytics, marketing providers under confidentiality and security obligations.</li>
          <li>International transfers: appropriate safeguards (e.g., SCCs) when transferring data from the EEA/Mexico to the U.S.</li>
          <li>We do not “sell” personal data under U.S. state privacy laws (e.g., CCPA/CPRA).</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Data subject rights</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Access, rectification, erasure, objection, restriction, portability (as applicable under GDPR/LFPDPPP).</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent and object to marketing.</li>
          <li>Opt-out of non-essential cookies and, where applicable, opt-out of “sale/sharing” under U.S. laws.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>To exercise rights: email <strong>privacy@mylightartgallery.com</strong> or write to the address above, including ID and the specific request.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Retention</h2>
        <p>We keep data as needed for the stated purposes or to meet legal obligations (tax, accounting, defense of claims).</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Cookies and similar tech</h2>
        <p>We use essential cookies and, with your consent, analytics/marketing cookies. Manage cookies via your browser or the consent banner when applicable.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Security</h2>
        <p>We implement reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect data from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Minors</h2>
        <p>The service is not directed to children under 16. If we detect minors’ data, we will delete it.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Updates</h2>
        <p>We will post any changes to this notice at https://www.mylightartgallery.com/en/privacy with the latest modification date.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<script>
  const privacySection = document.querySelector('.privacy');
  const header = document.querySelector('.site-header');
  const setHeaderOffset = () => {
    if (!privacySection || !header) return;
    privacySection.style.setProperty('--header-offset', `${header.offsetHeight}px`);
  };

  const handleScroll = () => {
    if (!privacySection) return;
    privacySection.classList.toggle('is-scrolled', window.scrollY > 40);
  };

  setHeaderOffset();
  handleScroll();
  window.addEventListener('resize', setHeaderOffset);
  window.addEventListener('scroll', handleScroll, { passive: true });
</script>

<style>
  .privacy {
    padding: 7rem 1.5rem 6rem;
    background: #e9e8e5;
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100vh;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .privacy::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: url('/logo/MY%20LIGHT%20ART%20GALLERY%20noirLOGO.png');
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-position: center 26%;
    background-size: clamp(320px, 110vw, 1200px);
    opacity: 0.12;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .privacy-scroll-fade {
    position: fixed;
    top: var(--header-offset, 140px);
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 210px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0));
    opacity: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .privacy.is-scrolled .privacy-scroll-fade {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .lead {
    text-align: center;
    color: #3a3631;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .card {
    background: transparent;
    padding: 1.75rem 0 0;
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18);
    box-shadow: none;
    border-radius: 0;
    color: #2f2b27;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .card:first-of-type {
    border-top: none;
    padding-top: 0;
  }

  ul {
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 0;
  }

  li {
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }

  strong {
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    h1 {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
    }

    .privacy::before {
      background-position: center 20%;
      background-size: clamp(280px, 140vw, 900px);
      opacity: 0.14;
    }

    .card {
      padding-top: 1.4rem;
    }
  }
</style>
